<br>
In any case, there will be a long period begininning in your forties where unless your twinked, insturment juggling is the way to go.<br>
<br>
Myself, I just got the equipment to fnally make a decent tank again (a couple of nice weapons, and CoF).  Without these I would undoubtly instrument juggle much more.<br>
<br>
Also at the high end game, when the situation is not dire or raid based, I tend to instrument juggle a while, use weapons &amp; sing, and back again.<br>
<br>
These are merely guidlines, every group and raid is different.  Don't buy into this beer commercial menatility.<br>
<br>
Use Weapons!<br>
Juggle Instruments!<br>
Use Weapons!<br>
Juggle Instruments!<br>
<br>
Our skils and songs are to varied to make one or the other the only joice.<br>
<br>
Good Luck,<br>
